The paper proposes a modification to the Perceptron algorithm, which is a popular algorithm in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of a focus of attention mechanism, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the Attentive Perceptron is designed to improve prediction accuracy, which is a common goal in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
